messages.messageBody:
I got a vaction lol.
ok well not a real one . I was at work last monday and suddnly wit5h out
warningboth ends went insane. hour later hubby came and got me i was still
vomiting and sotting on potty. hour after tahat it all turned to blood.
geee I decided to go to hosptial. they had me go in a plastic thing then I
had to argue with doctor that no I want having a "cycle" I had had a complete
histrorectomy 18 years ago. That was first time I got scared doctor got this
look and ordered all these test and all these other doctors started to come
in. giggle then i rembered I was at the unv. and it a teaching school. lol
well I got admitted was low on potasimun and was dehrated and they couldnt
stop the blood and they decided some where down the line I had ate
something that was bad. and that antibotics would make it worse. 6 days
latter still getting spoted blood and I went home. they want to wait it out
if not completely gone in another week I go back in . gee what fun.
so if I not here much that why this week I still dizzy and weak just sick of
hosptial food and miss home.
Dee
